        "description": "MULTIPLAYER UPDATE!\n\nCRUSH COMPETITION in an all-new multiplayer mode: Monster Mash! Fight players in Bay City and dodge thrown objects while stuffing your face full of people. Are you the king of the monsters?\n\nKAIJU-CASUAL in co-op free play! Mess around with buddies, hone your Kaiju skills, customize settings...heck, record your own monster movie and share it with us!\n\nDESTROY cities with your bare hands! Burn buildings! Toss tanks! Eat people! Block Buster is dedicated to every Kaiju movie you’ve ever watched.\n\nTEAR up the town with FIVE unique playable monsters: A giant ape, a radioactive lizard, a massive mecha, an angry prawn…or…a…butterfly…? Just go with it.\n\nRAMPAGE through destruction-based scavenger hunts in five unique cities, battling bosses and unlocking hidden paths.\n\nDone smashing? Build custom cosplay beasts in your ultimate Kaiju fan lair. Then invite friends over! \n\n· 2 all-new multiplayer game modes!\n· Fun \"monster sized\" weapons!\n· 5 unique, playable monsters!\n· 5 fully destructible cities!\n· Hidden items and secret paths!\n· Global leaderboards and 26 Meta Achievements!\n· Over 200 collectible items!\n· Avatar and monster customization!\n· Tweakable gameplay options for monsters of all sizes!\n· Awesome soundtrack by 8-bit Weapon and ComputeHer!",
